posting_body: ['Welcome to Hello Apartments', 'Rental Information', 'Pricing:', '$2030/Month | 2 Bedroom 2 Bath | 1085 sq ft', 'Lease Term:', '12-Month', 'show contact info', 'Apartment Amenities', '➢ Ceiling Fan', '➢ Efficient Appliances', '➢ Electronic Thermostat', '➢ Extra Storage', '➢ In-Home Laundry Room', '➢ Large Closets', '➢ Luxury Vinyl Plank Flooring', '➢ Patio/Balcony', '➢ Polished Quartz Countertops', '➢ Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Community Features', '➢ BBQ/Picnic Area', '➢ Business Center', '➢ Clubhouse', '➢ Courtyard', '➢ Dog Run', '➢ Fitness Center', '➢ Pool', '➢ Volleyball Court', '➢ Availability 24 Hours', '➢ Laundry Facilities', '➢ On-Site Maintenance', '➢ On-Site Management', '➢ Package Receiving', 'About Community', 'Description:', 'Offering well-designed one- and two-bedroom apartment homes with remarkable interior features such as polished quartz countertops and luxury vinyl plank flooring, and expansive walk-in closets- schedule an appointment to come and see for yourself.', "At Hello, you'll enjoy access to the city, unmatched urban amenities, and all the beauty of Golden Valley.", 'Enjoy an activity-filled weekend indoors or out.', 'Hello Apartments features a lobby bar and second-floor clubroom with games, comfortable seating as well as a full kitchen for private get-togethers or resident events such as cooking demos and holiday celebrations.', 'Hello is proudly managed by Peak Living.', 'At Peak Living, our mission is to provide the highest quality property management services in the industry.', 'We achieve this through our greatest asset;
